## Attribution

This project incorporates and extends the following design principles:
- Cosmic design system with stellar animations and gradient effects
- Constitutional framework for interplanetary governance
- Shadcn/ui component integration with custom theming
- Accessibility-first development with proper ARIA labels and keyboard navigation

The Starborn Dominion Constitution and associated governance principles contained
within this software are provided for educational and demonstration purposes,
representing a fictional framework for post-Earth civilization governance.